extends master-layout-fullwidth2

block pagetitle
  title Open House Events | Power Up Tech Academy

block metatag
  meta(description="Free public events to learn about our kids coding classes")

block content
  section
    .container.width-80-percent
      h2.heading-section.text-center FEBRUARY 19, 2017 OPEN HOUSE
      h4.heading-secondary.text-center Come visit us and try a free mini-lesson!
      p.text-center
        img(src="img/power-up-scratch-class.jpg" width="80%")
      
      p.pad-top-light Do you want to know more about coding for kids? Do you have questions about the differences between our classes? Are you wondering if your child will enjoy coding, or which class to put him/her in?

      p If the answer to any of these questions is "Yes", then you may want to come to our February Open House! At the Open House, you can:
      p
        ul.text-left.pad-left-heavy
          li
            i.fa.fa-bolt.fa-3.fa-secondary.pad-right-light
            | Bring your child to try out a mini coding class 
          li
            i.fa.fa-bolt.fa-3.fa-secondary.pad-right-light
            | Make a working project, just like we do in all our coding classes 
          li
            i.fa.fa-bolt.fa-3.fa-secondary.pad-right-light
            | Meet a teacher
          li
            i.fa.fa-bolt.fa-3.fa-secondary.pad-right-light
            | Check out our coding facility
          li
            i.fa.fa-bolt.fa-3.fa-secondary.pad-right-light
            | Ask questions

      p The open house is completely free, but since our space is limited we do require pre-registration.

      p.text-center.pad-top-light
        img(src="img/open-house-feb2017.png" width="80%" style="max-width:400px;")

      p.text-left.pad-top-light If you don't see the class you are interested in listed here, please 
        a(href="contact.html") contact us
        |  and we will coordinate with you to select the best time for you to come in.
 
             
      h3.heading-secondary.text-center.pad-top-light.pad-bottom-light SCROLL DOWN TO REGISTER
      
      p.text-center
        span.heading-secondary QUESTIONS?
        |  Call 773-382-0778 or
        a(href="../contact.html")  contact us online.
    
            
      
      script(type="text/javascript" src="https://bookeo.com/widget.js?a=315069PAHR14AEE213B9A&type=3150AJNA7F1532A97F63B")
           
  section.section-light
    .container
      .row
        .email-box.col-lg-6.col-lg-offset-3.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1
          #mc_embed_signup1
            form#mc-embedded-subscribe-form1.validate(action="//powerupta.us8.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=ed0abfd69c7573fb1e0291095&amp;id=b0ca742eea" method="post" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" target="_blank" novalidate)
              #mc_embed_signup_scroll1
                h2.heading-section SIGN UP FOR UPDATES
                p Be the first to find out about new classes, camps, special events and coding news:
                input#mce-EMAIL1.email(type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" placeholder="email address" required style="width:300px;")
                <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->
                div(style="position: absolute; left: -5000px;")
                  input(type="text" name="b_ed0abfd69c7573fb1e0291095_b0ca742eea" tabindex="-1" value="")
                input#mc-embedded-subscribe1.btn.btn-secondary(type="submit" value="Subscribe" name="subscribe")
                
         

  